    "text": [
        "Dear Mr. James,",
        "I am writing this letter to request you about the break I need from work for ten days and spend some family time.",
        "I am not finding time to spend time with children daily because of work pressures. Hence, I would like to plan for a holiday vacation for ten days, as my children have Diwali vacation for a period of fifteen days. To spend the quality time with family in a hectic schedule, I would like to ask you to grant me leave for ten days from 25th October to 5th November. Accordingly, we may book our tickets to Goa.",
        "During my absence, I would request one of my colleagues to handle the works. In case of emergency in technical issues if any, I will be available on call for the resolutions. I will be communicating through mails only when required.",
        "I would be grateful to you if leave is granted for a period of ten days. As soon as I return I will complete all my jobs at the earliest.",
        "Yours sincerely",
        "Goerge Thomas"
